The orange democratic movement (ODM) has now written a letter to the registrar of political parties in a bid to resolve the longstanding feud over political party&rsquo;s funds with its NASA siblings. Party secretary general Edwin Sifuna is asking the registrar of political parties to convene a meeting and address the issue that has in recent times threatened to kill the NASA coalition that brought together ODM, ANC, Ford Kenya and wiper party. So, is this a way of bringing together the former allies ahead of the 2022 general election?
